        <p>Adesso <strong>(vai)</strong> <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-24 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="va'" data-correct-answer="va'"> a chiamare tutti i tuoi amici e poi <strong>(dai)</strong> <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-24 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="da'" data-correct-answer="da'"> a ciascuno una fetta di torta.</p>
